<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.8">
<l>muṉṉula kaṅka ḷēḻu miruḷmaṇṭi yuṇṇa mutalōṭu vīṭu maṟiyā</l>
<l>teṉṉitu vanta teṉṉa vimaiyōrti kaippa veḻilvēta miṉṟi maṟaiya</l>
<l>piṉṉaiyum vāṉa varkkum muṉivarkkum nalki yiruḷtīrntiv vaiya makiḻa</l>
<l>vaṉṉama tāyi runtaṅ kaṟanūlu raitta vatunammai yāḷu maracē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Long ago, when darkness had oppressed the seven worlds,</l>
<l rend="indent">so the celestials were bewildered,</l>
<l>As they wondered, “What has occurred?” not knowing its beginning and end,</l>
<l>When the elegant Vedas, being missing, were hidden,</l>
<l rend="indent">that which then pronounced the book of virtues,</l>
<l rend="indent">furthermore granting [it] to the sages and celestials,</l>
<l>Ending the darkness so this earth rejoiced, having become a swan,</l>
<l rend="indent">is the sovereign who rules us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
